qas.question: What is expected to have an effect on migration timing?
What have studies shown regarding climate change?
What else is climate change been shown to change?

answers.text: breeding as well as population variations

context: Large scale <a0_0>climatic changes<a0_0/>, as have been experienced in the past, are expected to have an effect on the timing of migration. Studies have shown a variety of effects including <a1_0>timing changes in migration<a1_0/>, <a2_0>breeding as well as population variations<a2_0/>.
